  ('dietitian-moex-11227', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '缺少下列何種胞器（organelles），則細胞絕大部分之能量供應將會立即中止？ 核膜 (nuclear membrane)  高基氏體 (Golgi apparatus)  粒線體 (mitochondria)  溶小體 (lysosomes)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11228', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'γ胺基丁酸（GABA；r-aminobutyrate）之作用主要是為打開何種離子通道？ Ca++  Cl-  Mg++  Na+', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11229', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '出現下列何現象會使肺部呼出大量的CO？ 2 呼吸性酸中毒  呼吸性鹼中毒  代謝性酸中毒  代謝性鹼中毒', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11230', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '腦波訊號中若反覆出現大幅波動（可高至1000μV）及單獨出現之尖峰放電的情形，則此人可能有下列何種病症？ 燥狂症（mania）    精神分裂症（schizophrenia） 巴金森氏症（Parkinson’s disease）  癲癇（epilepsy）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11231', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當血漿中鈣離子濃度下降時，會引發下列何種情況？ 甲狀腺素分泌增加  維生素D 合成減少  抑制腎臟對磷酸鹽的再吸收  增加腸胃道對磷酸鹽的吸收 3', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11232', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '人類注射MPTP（1-methyl-4-phenyl-1,2,3,6-tetrahydropyridine）之後，主要會導致何種現象？ 類似舞蹈症現象    基底核(basal ganglia)內多巴胺(dopamine)含量明顯的減少 體溫升高    甲狀腺（thyroid gland）萎縮', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
